    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as expected, making it a dependable choice for a daily driver. While the exterior and interior are clean, you may find some minor signs of wear such as small stone chips on the hood and slight creasing on the driver's seat leather. All major systems are functional, and it has a solid service history, offering a great balance of quality and value.",
