    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, with only minor, age-appropriate stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the rear bumper that is barely visible from a distance. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has been kept smoke-free and pet-free; the leather seats are firm and supportive, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and the high-fidelity infotainment system, is in perfect working order. Mechanically, the car is sound, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced exclusively with synthetic oil. We recently replaced the brake pads and performed a multi-point inspection to ensure it is road-ready. The tires have roughly 70% tread remaining, providing excellent traction for the seasons ahead. This is a solid, honest car that has been garaged and cared for, offering a premium driving experience without the 'new car' price tag.",
      "price": 32500.0,
